title.rendered: AMBU Skin Prep Pads – Box of 500 PCS

content.rendered: Skin Prep Pads are abrasive pads suited for skin prepping. The product has an adhesive backing to be applied to the finger.

excerpt.rendered:
• The product is easily applied on the finger due to the adhesive and shape.
  • Abrasive pad / 19 x 28 mm
